{
  "title": "LeadCore API 对接文档",
  "children": [
    {
      "id": "overview",
      "title": "概述",
      "content": "<h1>概述</h1><p>LeadCore 为开发者提供一套完整的云端后端服务 API，支持 Android、iOS、Windows 及微信小程序。所有接口均基于 HTTPS 协议，采用 RESTful 风格设计。</p><h2>基础信息</h2><table><tr><th>项目</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>API 域名</td><td><code>https://api.leadcore.com</code></td></tr><tr><td>请求格式</td><td>application/json</td></tr><tr><td>响应格式</td><td>application/json</td></tr><tr><td>字符编码</td><td>UTF-8</td></tr></table><h2>公共响应结构</h2><p>所有接口统一返回以下格式：</p><pre><code>{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"success\\\",\\n  \\\"data\\\": { ... }\\n}</code></pre><div class='block-note'><strong>说明：</strong> code 为 200 表示成功，其他值表示错误，具体错误码请参考错误码章节。</div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "auth",
      "title": "鉴权机制",
      "content": "<h1>鉴权机制</h1><p>所有 API 请求（除登录、注册外）都需要在 HTTP Header 中携带 Access Token 进行身份验证。</p><h2>获取 Token</h2><p>调用 <code>/api/auth/login</code> 接口，使用用户名和密码换取 Access Token 和 Refresh Token。</p><h3>请求头示例</h3><pre><code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;your_access_token&gt;</code></pre><h2>Token 有效期</h2><ul><li><strong>Access Token</strong>：有效期 2 小时，过期后需使用 Refresh Token 刷新。</li><li><strong>Refresh Token</strong>：有效期 7 天，过期后需重新登录。</li></ul><div class='block-warn'><strong>注意：</strong> 请妥善保管你的账号密码，避免泄露。</div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "user",
      "title": "用户模块",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "user-login",
          "title": "用户登录",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/api/auth/login",
          "params": [
            { "name": "username", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "用户名" },
            { "name": "password", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "密码" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"accessToken\\\": \\\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\\\",\\n    \\\"refreshToken\\\": \\\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\\\",\\n    \\\"expiresIn\\\": 7200\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "登录成功后请妥善保存 accessToken，后续请求需在 Header 中携带。"
        },
        {
          "id": "user-register",
          "title": "用户注册",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/api/auth/register",
          "params": [
            { "name": "username", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "用户名，4-20 位字母或数字" },
            { "name": "password", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "密码，6-32 位" },
            { "name": "email", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "邮箱地址" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"注册成功，请前往邮箱激活账号\\\"\\n}",
          "remark": "注册后需前往邮箱点击激活链接，账号方可正常使用。"
        },
        {
          "id": "user-profile",
          "title": "获取用户信息",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/api/user/current",
          "params": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "Bearer {accessToken}，需在 Header 中传递" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"id\\\": 1,\\n    \\\"username\\\": \\\"dev_user\\\",\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"dev@leadcore.com\\\",\\n    \\\"avatar\\\": \\\"https://cdn.leadcore.com/avatars/1.png\\\",\\n    \\\"createdAt\\\": \\\"2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\\\"\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "需要携带 accessToken 进行身份验证。"
        },
        {
          "id": "user-update",
          "title": "更新用户信息",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/api/user/current",
          "params": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "Bearer {accessToken}，需在 Header 中传递" },
            { "name": "email", "type": "string", "required": false, "desc": "新邮箱地址" },
            { "name": "avatar", "type": "string", "required": false, "desc": "头像 URL" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"更新成功\\\",\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"id\\\": 1,\\n    \\\"username\\\": \\\"dev_user\\\",\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"new@email.com\\\",\\n    \\\"avatar\\\": \\\"https://cdn.leadcore.com/avatars/1.png\\\"\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "仅需传递需要修改的字段，未传递的字段保持不变。"
        },
        {
          "id": "user-refresh",
          "title": "刷新 Token",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/api/auth/refresh",
          "params": [
            { "name": "refreshToken", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "登录时返回的 refreshToken" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"accessToken\\\": \\\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\\\",\\n    \\\"expiresIn\\\": 7200\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "当 accessToken 过期时，使用 refreshToken 换取新的 accessToken。refreshToken 有效期为 7 天。"
        },
        {
          "id": "user-logout",
          "title": "退出登录",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/api/auth/logout",
          "params": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "Bearer {accessToken}，需在 Header 中传递" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"退出成功\\\"\\n}",
          "remark": "退出后当前 accessToken 将立即失效。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "storage",
      "title": "数据存储",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "storage-create",
          "title": "创建数据",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/api/storage/{tableName}",
          "params": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "Bearer {accessToken}，需在 Header 中传递" },
            { "name": "tableName", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "数据表名称（路径参数）" },
            { "name": "body", "type": "object", "required": true, "desc": "数据内容，JSON 格式" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"id\\\": \\\"rec_xxxxxx\\\",\\n    \\\"createdAt\\\": \\\"2026-07-15T10:30:00Z\\\"\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "表需提前在控制台创建，字段类型与数据内容匹配。"
        },
        {
          "id": "storage-query",
          "title": "查询数据",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/api/storage/{tableName}",
          "params": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "Bearer {accessToken}，需在 Header 中传递" },
            { "name": "tableName", "type": "string", "required": true, "desc": "数据表名称（路径参数）" },
            { "name": "page", "type": "int", "required": false, "desc": "页码，默认 1" },
            { "name": "limit", "type": "int", "required": false, "desc": "每页条数，默认 20，最大 100" },
            { "name": "sort", "type": "string", "required": false, "desc": "排序字段，如 -createdAt 表示倒序" },
            { "name": "filter", "type": "string", "required": false, "desc": "JSON 过滤条件，如 {\\\"age\\\":{\\\"$gt\\\":18}}" }
          ],
          "response": "{\\n  \\\"code\\\": 200,\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"items\\\": [\\n      { \\\"id\\\": \\\"rec_001\\\", \\\"name\\\": \\\"张三\\\", \\\"age\\\": 28 },\\n      { \\\"id\\\": \\\"rec_002\\\", \\\"name\\\": \\\"李四\\\", \\\"age\\\": 32 }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"total\\\": 100,\\n    \\\"page\\\": 1,\\n    \\\"limit\\\": 20\\n  }\\n}",
          "remark": "支持分页、排序和条件过滤，filter 使用 MongoDB 风格查询语法。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "errors",
      "title": "错误码",
      "content": "<h1>错误码说明</h1><p>当接口返回的 <code>code</code> 不为 200 时，请根据以下错误码定位问题。</p><table><tr><th>错误码</th><th>含义</th></tr><tr><td>400</td><td>请求参数错误</td></tr><tr><td>401</td><td>未认证或 Token 无效</td></tr><tr><td>403</td><td>权限不足</td></tr><tr><td>404</td><td>资源不存在</td></tr><tr><td>429</td><td>请求频率超限</td></tr><tr><td>500</td><td>服务器内部错误</td></tr><tr><td>1001</td><td>用户名或密码错误</td></tr><tr><td>1002</td><td>账号未激活</td></tr><tr><td>1003</td><td>Refresh Token 已过期</td></tr><tr><td>2001</td><td>数据表不存在</td></tr><tr><td>2002</td><td>记录不存在</td></tr><tr><td>3001</td><td>文件上传失败</td></tr><tr><td>4001</td><td>推送目标不可达</td></tr></table>"
    }
  ]
}
